<div id="descriptionmodule" class="module toggle-wrap">
    <div class="mod-header">
        <h3 class="toggle-title">Description</h3>
    </div>
    <div id="issue-description" class="mod-content">
        <p>Authentication with both shibboleth and local accounts was possible in previous versions of the authenticator. We are certainly not the only ones who would need that, and incorporating the feature should be easy as it worked previously without any problems.  </p>
    </div>
</div>





                    
                        






